ass todo append - Append TEXT to the todo.txt file

Usage:
  ass todo append [TEXT] [OPTIONS]
  ass todo append --help | -h

Options:
  --todotxt-file, -f FILE
    The location of the todo.txt file

  --verbose, -v (repeatable)
    Set the verbosity level

  --help, -h
    Show this help

Arguments:
  TEXT


Environment Variables:
  TODOTXT_FILE
    The location of the todo.txt file
    Default: /home/lgrassauer/todo/todo.txt
